897
01:24:14,020 --> 01:24:15,520
I didn't hear you say anything.

898
01:24:18,340 --> 01:24:22,039
We happen to have a form of an army around this building anyway, as you know.

899
01:24:24,240 --> 01:24:26,159
Abdullah Arik is listening, that's who we have.

900
01:24:27,539 --> 01:24:34,460
And he is the very person who comes because he would lead you with a hadith,

901
01:24:34,539 --> 01:24:38,000
A brother came to see us, he just had a dream and he doesn't know.

902
01:24:38,399 --> 01:24:43,399
Anyway, what I want to tell you is that people like the details, it's fine.

903
01:24:49,539 --> 01:24:54,520
There are invisible forces around us, we don't need to do anything.

904
01:24:54,979 --> 01:25:05,600
This age is an age of mental, mental debate, rather than the force of fighting.

905
01:25:11,879 --> 01:25:16,520
Anyway, you can't fight because of that, over that, or whatever you want to call it.

906
01:25:17,720 --> 01:25:19,239
Unless you are attacked, anyway.

907
01:25:19,840 --> 01:25:21,119
It's not a big deal.

908
01:25:22,199 --> 01:25:22,859
No, it's not a big deal.

909
01:25:26,819 --> 01:25:31,859
Well, aggression is one thing, and fighting is something else.

910
01:25:33,459 --> 01:25:38,720
I mean, they join the army, of course, but they don't fight. Because that's a job, allowed by God Almighty, to earn a living.

911
01:25:39,000 --> 01:25:44,380
It's for a living. A job is a means of supporting you to earn an honest living.

912
01:25:45,539 --> 01:25:54,859
If you join any institution just to earn a living, you have to know what that institution is involved in.

913
01:25:56,740 --> 01:25:58,619
Yeah, but you don't know what it is that you're doing.

914
01:25:58,640 --> 01:26:02,920
You don't know whether you're living off selling liquor, for example, which is breaking God's law.

915
01:26:04,160 --> 01:26:10,779
He's asking about joining the armed forces, but if you join the armed forces and there's no war, it's just like any job.

916
01:26:11,800 --> 01:26:15,159
Well, suppose your government gets in a war with another country in the area.

917
01:26:15,420 --> 01:26:18,319
That's when you have to make a decision whether it is for God or not.

918
01:26:30,400 --> 01:26:38,279
Well, suppose you're working for a big company, and they're producing something, you know,

919
01:26:38,279 --> 01:26:48,220
like, you know, or, say, napalm, which you may be working on, you know, maybe you're not

920
01:26:48,220 --> 01:26:52,739
You're not directly involved in the manufacturing, but you are a part of that company.

921
01:26:52,739 --> 01:26:56,579
There's no war, it's perfectly all right. But the command is to prepare for war.

922
01:26:58,000 --> 01:27:00,140
Prepare the maximum power that you have.

923
01:27:02,920 --> 01:27:07,560
War, that is, aggression, is forbidden; that's a big responsibility.

924
01:27:09,920 --> 01:27:16,020
So joining the armed forces, or making weapons, or anything, is not war.

925
01:27:18,320 --> 01:27:22,619
If it is war, then you have to make a decision if it is for God's cause or not.

926
01:27:22,840 --> 01:27:25,380
So it's a case of having a nuclear army.

